[http://www.fortinet.com/products/fortiap/112B.html Product page]
[http://www.fortinet.com/sites/default/files/productdatasheets/FortiAP-112B.pdf Datasheet] "ERA150-0.30 LFP" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. The FCC label shows the device with an 00:09:0F ('''Fortinet''') OUI. The manual specifies that this device is powered using the included EPE-1212 injector and power adapter. The UPC for this product may be 094922405302 (FAP-112B-A). Per the manual, the default SSID and (presumed wireless) password ( / PSK) is '''fortinet.mesh.root'''. ==Images== Image:Fortinet_FAP-112B_Lt.png|left Image:Fortinet_FAP-112B_Rt-Up.png|right up Image:Fortinet_FAP-112B_Rt.png|right Image:Fortinet_FAP-112B_top.png|top Image:Fortinet_FAP-112B_Bk.png|back [[Has images::external| ]]
